{"type": "article", "id": 30865, "title": "买个柜子，还能随意改变面板的形状组合｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-08-10T23:02:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 31357, "name": "Manchuen Hui Design"}, {"id": 31358, "name": "Cody Moore"}, {"id": 31359, "name": "Ákos Huber"}, {"id": 31360, "name": "Ana Barbu"}, {"id": 31361, "name": "Raiane Girotto"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 106, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160811000936JuOfPwV1Fq6UmbCy.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Dong Stool by Manchuen Hui Design</h3><p>以路边大排档所使用的凳子为灵感，香港的 <a href=\"http://www.manchuen-hui.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Manchuen Hui Design</a> 设计了这把透露出极简美学的三脚凳 <a href=\"http://www.manchuen-hui.com/projects/dong-stool\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dong Stool</a>。凳面是一块圆形的木板，它的凳腿则由三根弯曲的金属横梁组合而成，通过金属扣在底部进行固定。整张凳子仅包含七个组件，组装起来非常容易。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001327Moe0hsfIlN8r9qPa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001327RbzT3BHZuxS1IK9n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707619\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001328YEBJC7slX1FRk3b8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001327fIyGSJ5j8kvnCqFW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001328gQvUtWxPmFNkH02e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608110013289V3O2gNBEY1HZUax.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Datelight by Cody Moore</h3><p>你会选择用什么方式提醒自己不要错过纪念日？在手机上设置提醒的确是一种简单快捷的方法，但如果是要纪念某些特殊的时刻，你可以尝试用一种更特别的方式。由 Cody Moore 设计的 Datelight 就是专门为纪念日而打造的智能灯具，平时它只有内圈才会发光，到了设定好的纪念日它的外圈也会跟着发光，而且灯光的强弱是根据用户为纪念日设置的重要程度而决定的。如果用户不小心忘记当天究竟是为了纪念什么，只需要顺时针转动 Datelight 的圆环，这一天的详细信息就会慢慢浮现出来。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608110014050HE3jh2zqFfl68BD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001405Kd6uNtsFiZb7nlVp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001404MkWOA4yeCTJtUKPR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001405TOY9qBoRU2uGakid.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001404QJE0jRlv3a17ILhA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Wing Sofa by Ákos Huber</h3><p>在参观了卢浮宫博物馆之后，<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/akoshuber\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ákos Huber</a> 以大理石雕塑胜利女神像（Nike of Samothrace）为灵感设计了这款名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/41353891/Wing-SofaInspired-by-Nike-of-Samothrace\" rel=\"nofollow\">Wing</a> 的沙发。它的框架由山毛榉木制作而成，经由曲木工艺打造出了像女神翅膀那样流畅的线条。为了还原那种轻盈的感觉，Huber 舍弃了普通的坐垫，采用 6 毫米宽的攀岩绳将开口两侧连接起来，既是座位又起到加固整体结构的作用。这种独特的搭配让人感受到一股优雅的力量，使 Wing 很容易就成为房间里最引人注目的家具。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001226OEXBRQ9V5LkYUtPS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.642188\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001225tqNGSDeJavfCVy9L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.676667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001225iokvRVSH2gyIhTq3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001226y4MLWzENIkDa2rO8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.566667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608110012268R9ab3TiynjEPhoq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001226jizFYLA5kNEO9uoZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>C# Sideboard by Ana Barbu</h3><p>就算不是几何控，你也很难不被罗马尼亚设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/anabarbu\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ana Barbu</a> 带来的这件 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/40936691/C\" rel=\"nofollow\">C# Sideboard</a> 餐具柜所吸引：Barbu 并没有为它设计市面上常见的柜门，当你需要取放餐具时只需要滑动菱形遮板即可。遮板分为三种颜色，均由 20 根倾斜的金属构成，巧妙地将背后的餐具隐藏起来。上下两层有着独立的轨道，你可以移动遮板，或是将它们取出重新分配位置，组合出不同的几何图案。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001150K1IxyJa0N5gdFk3i.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001149sYR3mMCyXSogZ4pV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001149ncF7DysHh56VfOpj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001149UGBPjtM1TmkIxOec.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001149t8hGgERZir3cBMAN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.940000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001149ZsKzp4o1vjAamLMI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Vinyl Clock by Nick Ponomarenko &amp; Tanya Korostel</h3><p>老黑胶唱片可以换一种方式重生。Nick Ponomarenko 和 Tanya Korostel 这两位设计师就根据四个不同的主题将这些唱片改造成造型独特的挂钟，用户在购买时还可以订制表盘的造型和颜色。如果你对这个系列感兴趣，可以通过<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/new-life-of-vinyl#/\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买，单价为 25 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001102e5b3SVnvRPs60TgK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001103gIOhNSY1jfmXVoGT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001102D5IMPpsX6W93Abni.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001104tVfT5byx7ApJ0jo4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608110011037Z3qjygVhr6cY09m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001103qzxNXjTSdlOVeQUr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Bendito Choco by Raiane Girotto</h3><p>巴西的设计系学生 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/raianegt\" rel=\"nofollow\">Raiane Girotto</a> 为手工巧克力品牌 Bendito Choco 设计了一组以大理石纹为主题的包装。大理石纹所特有的质感就好像还未成型的液态巧克力，使用的配色则与五种口味一一对应。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608110010219825yIYABOEMt4ie.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.642857\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001014GLaemx5oTvWPSKzN.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.642857\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001019BGOeQKrSydlLYCsj.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.642857\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001020wQrdbkVMJicOElC5.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.571429\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001022oGme10n5fEDCHvOc.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.571429\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811001022jGsVUSDBh758lFfN.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.571429\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div>"}